data.description: Check out this renovated frame 2 flat. Perfect to occupy the 2nd unit and use the current rent from unit 1 to help with the mortgage .Both units have 2 beds and 1 bath. Many updates ! Newer plumbing, electrical, storm doors, furnaces, HWT, bathrooms, kitchen fixtures, windows and siding. Laminate flooring throughout living areas, bathrooms and kitchens ceramic tile floors. Fence backyard . Check with IHDA for downpayment assistance programs.  Schedule your appointment.
